The Mines at Everwinter 04

Level 4

General
HistoryThe dungeon was created by a chaotic good rogue as a mine. It was eventually abandoned due to plague, and has lain empty for many years until recently.
WallsHewn Stone (DC 20 to climb)
FloorSmooth Stone
TemperatureCool
IlluminationDark (individual creatures may carry lights)
